{"tid":47161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［賊贓歸還］解放軍中午已交還美國無人水底探測器","createTime":"2016-12-20T07:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T08:55:52.000Z","uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a39124ae4b35e73a4055f508d93044fd2f5e5a0","tid":47161,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:12:42.000Z","msg":"中國國防部在其官方微博上公佈，今日中午在南海「有關海域」順利完成美國無人水底探測器的移交工作，但微博中未有透露移交的地點、水底探測器的狀況及負責交接的雙方人員。<br />\n美國國防部官員較早前表示，要求中國歸還在南海搶走的無人水底探測器的商討，取得進展，預料中方最快會在今日交還，而路透社則引述美國官員稱，解放軍將會在黃岩島附近水域，將無人水底探測器交還美軍軍艦。<br />\n解放軍在上周四（15日）在南海搶走美國的無人水底探測器，當時軍方聲稱這個是「不明裝置」，以「為預防發生航行安全問題」為藉口，對探測器移走「進行識別查證」。<br />\n美國總統當選人特朗普事發後稱，中國的「偷竊行為」是前所未有，更揚言「讓他們（中國）留着吧」（let them keep it）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161220/56069330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161220%2F56069330&d=oC5AbjMi%2BH1TB6WHdjrt%2FZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8af28bd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161220%2F56069330&h=3ed35f29\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161220/56069330</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個乜鳩支那少將又話長keep既"},{"pid":"6f3fa2d942f76bac59d8a3016a8f6d3bed741184","tid":47161,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:13:58.000Z","msg":"偷竊大國 &mdash; 死支那。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8e0bbd32c9487e356629e7b750d7a914d77030","tid":47161,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:14:09.000Z","msg":"驚比美國佬搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"121c7baff17ac7d16f7960930e7e648669a2ed2d","tid":47161,"uid":57657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"死支那"},{"pid":"32adc843d2e8a3538c039e03611fd7d3e633f90b","tid":47161,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">當時軍方聲稱這個是「不明裝置」，以「為預防發生航行安全問題」為藉口，對探測器移走「進行識別查證」</span><br />\n<br />\n同平時啲支那拐子婆，拐人地個細路，然後話見佢一個人喺街，我幫佢搵老豆老母咋。<br />\n<br />\n有咩政府就有咩人民。<br />\n<br />\n垃撚圾國家。"},{"pid":"6d818cb5c482cb786fd785b2be214566c4a24578","tid":47161,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"留名睇美國專家話部野俾人拆過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92e7e9b1f122100c9fa0874ff96407f15ca62b6","tid":47161,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚比美國佬搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要有籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}